page","contentId":"urn:bbc:cps:3c244d23-2e54-4557-a8b2-dba76beb4d4b","section":"uk","producer":"NEWS","additionalProperties":{"custom_var_1":"2020-10-08T10:08:58.000Z","custom_var_2":"2020-10-08T19:34:38.000Z"}}},"indexImage":{"alt":"Bartender","src":"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1024/branded_news/13A93/production/_114813508_gettyimages-1224649294.jpg","width":976,"height":549},"section":{"name":"UK","uri":"/news/uk"},"site":{"name":"BBC News","uri":"/news"},"timestampRelative":"5 days ago","publishedDateTime":"2020-10-08T19:34:38.000Z","translations":{"seeAlsos":"More on this story","tagList":"Related Topics"}},"headline":"Covid-19: New restrictions to be announced for parts of England 'within days' - Jenrick","contributor":null,"blocks":[{"type":"image","model":{"emphasiseImage":true,"copyright":"Getty Images","media":{"__typename":"ComponentsImage","src":"https://c.files.bbci.co.uk/161A3/production/_114813509_gettyimages-1224649294.jpg","srcSet":"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/161A3/production/_114813509_gettyimages-1224649294.jpg 240w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/161A3/production/_114813509_gettyimages-1224649294.jpg 320w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/161A3/production/_114813509_gettyimages-1224649294.jpg 480w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/161A3/production/_114813509_gettyimages-1224649294.jpg 624w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/161A3/production/_114813509_gettyimages-1224649294.jpg 800w","height":549,"width":976,"alt":"Bartender","loading":"lazy"}}},{"type":"text","model":{"blocks":[{"type":"paragraph","model":{"text":"New measures to tackle coronavirus are to be announced \"in the coming days\", a minister says, after the BBC was told pubs and restaurants could be closed in the worst-affected areas of England. ","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"New measures to tackle coronavirus are to be announced \"in the coming days\", a minister says, after the BBC was told pubs and restaurants could be closed in the worst-affected areas of England. ","attributes":["bold"]}}]}}]}},{"type":"text","model":{"blocks":[{"type":"paragraph","model":{"text":"There could also be a ban on overnight stays away from home in the locations  - which include the North and Midlands.","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"There could also be a ban on overnight stays away from home in the locations  - which include the North and Midlands.","attributes":[]}}]}}]}},{"type":"text","model":{"blocks":[{"type":"paragraph","model":{"text":"Communities Secretary Robert Jenrick said the government was \"currently considering what steps to take\".","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"Communities Secretary Robert Jenrick said the government was \"currently considering what steps to take\".","attributes":[]}}]}}]}},{"type":"text","model":{"blocks":[{"type":"paragraph","model":{"text":"A three-tier system for local lockdowns is also likely to be announced. ","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"A ","attributes":[]}},{"type":"urlLink","model":{"text":"three-tier system for local lockdowns","locator":"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-54371943","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"three-tier system for local lockdowns","attributes":[]}}]}},{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":" is also likely to be announced. ","attributes":[]}}]}}]}},{"type":"text","model":{"blocks":[{"type":"paragraph","model":{"text":"Under the system, different parts of the country would be placed in different categories - although ministers are still discussing the precise details of the toughest level of restrictions over the next couple of days.","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"Under the system, different parts of the country would be placed in different categories - although ministers are still discussing the precise details of the toughest level of restrictions over the next couple of days.","attributes":[]}}]}}]}},{"type":"text","model":{"blocks":[{"type":"paragraph","model":{"text":"A final decision on the time period or extent of potential closures has not yet been made and a formal announcement is not likely to come until Monday, BBC political editor Laura Kuenssberg said.","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"A final decision on the time period or extent of potential closures has not yet been made and a formal announcement is not likely to come until Monday, BBC political editor Laura Kuenssberg said.","attributes":[]}}]}}]}},{"type":"text","model":{"blocks":[{"type":"paragraph","model":{"text":"It comes as North of England and Midlands MPs have been briefed by health ministers and chief medical officer Chris Whitty about the latest coronavirus data.","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"It comes as North of England and Midlands MPs have been ","attributes":[]}},{"type":"urlLink","model":{"text":"briefed by health ministers and chief medical officer","locator":"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-derbyshire-54464470","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"briefed by health ministers and chief medical officer","attributes":[]}}]}},{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":" Chris Whitty about the latest coronavirus data.","attributes":[]}}]}}]}},{"type":"text","model":{"blocks":[{"type":"paragraph","model":{"text":"The number of people in the UK to have tested positive for coronavirus rose by 17,540 - an increase of 3,378 on Wednesday's figures - with a further 77 deaths reported.","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"The number of people in the UK to have tested positive for coronavirus rose by 17,540 - an increase of 3,378 on Wednesday's figures - with a further 77 deaths reported.","attributes":[]}}]}}]}},{"type":"text","model":{"blocks":[{"type":"paragraph","model":{"text":"Some politicians in the North of England and the Midlands have shared their frustration about the plans appearing in newspapers before being announced in Parliament. ","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"Some politicians in the North of England and the Midlands ","attributes":[]}},{"type":"urlLink","model":{"text":"have shared their frustration about the plans appearing in newspapers before being announced in Parliament","locator":"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-derbyshire-54464470","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"have shared their frustration about the plans appearing in newspapers before being announced in Parliament","attributes":[]}}]}},{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":". ","attributes":[]}}]}}]}},{"type":"text","model":{"blocks":[{"type":"paragraph","model":{"text":"The Labour mayor of Greater Manchester, Andy Burnham, told the BBC: \"If it's urgent, give us the detail, give us the evidence behind the proposals. Let's discuss it and let's agree it quickly.\"","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"The Labour mayor of Greater Manchester, Andy Burnham, told the BBC: \"If it's urgent, give us the detail, give us the evidence behind the proposals. Let's discuss it and let's agree it quickly.\"","attributes":[]}}]}}]}},{"type":"unorderedList","model":{"blocks":[{"type":"listItem","model":{"blocks":[{"type":"urlLink","model":{"text":"Check the Covid rules where you live","locator":"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-54373904","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"Check the Covid rules where you live","attributes":[]}}]}}]}},{"type":"listItem","model":{"blocks":[{"type":"urlLink","model":{"text":"What is the risk of Covid overwhelming the NHS?","locator":"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/health-54440392","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"What is the risk of Covid overwhelming the NHS?","attributes":[]}}]}}]}},{"type":"listItem","model":{"blocks":[{"type":"urlLink","model":{"text":"Do local lockdowns stop the spread of Covid?","locator":"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/health-54239538","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"Do local lockdowns stop the spread of Covid?","attributes":[]}}]}}]}},{"type":"listItem","model":{"blocks":[{"type":"urlLink","model":{"text":"London local lockdown 'unlikely this week'","locator":"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-54461871","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"London local lockdown 'unlikely this week'","attributes":[]}}]}}]}},{"type":"listItem","model":{"blocks":[{"type":"urlLink","model":{"text":"Further 1,600 students test positive for Covid","locator":"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-tyne-54468127","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"Further 1,600 students test positive for Covid","attributes":[]}}]}}]}}]}},{"type":"text","model":{"blocks":[{"type":"paragraph","model":{"text":"Meanwhile, Labour has challenged the government to publish the scientific evidence behind the 22:00 BST closing time for pubs and restaurants in England. ","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"Meanwhile, Labour has challenged the government to publish the scientific evidence behind the 22:00 BST closing time for pubs and restaurants in England. ","attributes":[]}}]}}]}},{"type":"text","model":{"blocks":[{"type":"paragraph","model":{"text":"Leader Sir Keir Starmer said his party would not be \"voting down\" the measure in the Commons next Tuesday but the policy \"needs to be reformed\". ","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"Leader Sir Keir Starmer ","attributes":[]}},{"type":"urlLink","model":{"text":"said his party would not be \"voting down\" the measure in the Commons next Tuesday","locator":"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-54466398","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"said his party would not be \"voting down\" the measure in the Commons next Tuesday","attributes":[]}}]}},{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":" but the policy \"needs to be reformed\". ","attributes":[]}}]}}]}},{"type":"image","model":{"emphasiseImage":false,"media":{"__typename":"ComponentsImage","src":"https://c.files.bbci.co.uk/2829/production/_114818201_optimised-uk_daily_cases_with_ra_8oct-nc.png","srcSet":"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/2829/production/_114818201_optimised-uk_daily_cases_with_ra_8oct-nc.png 240w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/2829/production/_114818201_optimised-uk_daily_cases_with_ra_8oct-nc.png 320w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/2829/production/_114818201_optimised-uk_daily_cases_with_ra_8oct-nc.png 480w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/2829/production/_114818201_optimised-uk_daily_cases_with_ra_8oct-nc.png 624w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/2829/production/_114818201_optimised-uk_daily_cases_with_ra_8oct-nc.png 800w","height":1875,"width":2666,"alt":"Graph showing UK daily Covid cases on 8 October 2020","loading":"lazy"}}},{"type":"text","model":{"blocks":[{"type":"paragraph","model":{"text":"Downing Street said that early data suggested a \"significant proportion\" of coronavirus exposure was seen in the hospitality sector, especially in younger age groups. ","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"Downing Street said that early data suggested a \"significant proportion\" of coronavirus exposure was seen in the hospitality sector, especially in younger age groups. ","attributes":[]}}]}}]}},{"type":"text","model":{"blocks":[{"type":"paragraph","model":{"text":"But pressed on whether the government would publish evidence on the issue, Mr Jenrick told the BBC: \"It is commonsensical that the longer you stay in pubs and restaurants, the more likely you are to come into contact with other individuals.","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"But pressed on whether the government would publish evidence on the issue, Mr Jenrick told the BBC: \"It is commonsensical that the longer you stay in pubs and restaurants, the more likely you are to come into contact with other individuals.","attributes":[]}}]}}]}},{"type":"text","model":{"blocks":[{"type":"paragraph","model":{"text":"\"The more drinks that people have, the more likely that some people are to break the rules.\"","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"\"The more drinks that people have, the more likely that some people are to break the rules.\"","attributes":[]}}]}}]}},{"type":"text","model":{"blocks":[{"type":"paragraph","model":{"text":"He added that it was right to \"take action decisively, rather than waiting for the most detailed epidemiological evidence to emerge\". ","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"He added that it was right to \"take action decisively, rather than waiting for the most detailed epidemiological evidence to emerge\". ","attributes":[]}}]}}]}},{"type":"text","model":{"blocks":[{"type":"paragraph","model":{"text":"On the possibility of additional restrictions for some parts of England, Mr Jenrick did not rule out pubs being closed but said the response would be \"proportionate and localised\".","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"On the possibility of additional restrictions for some parts of England, Mr Jenrick did not rule out pubs being closed but said the response would be \"proportionate and localised\".","attributes":[]}}]}}]}},{"type":"text","model":{"blocks":[{"type":"paragraph","model":{"text":"He added the government was trying to give \"greater consistency on rules so they're easier to understand\" and was working on \"slightly broader canvases of regions or cities and counties to avoid differences in people's daily lives if they drive over the border\". ","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"He added the government was trying to give \"greater consistency on rules so they're easier to understand\" and was working on \"slightly broader canvases of regions or cities and counties to avoid differences in people's daily lives if they drive over the border\". ","attributes":[]}}]}}]}},{"type":"image","model":{"emphasiseImage":false,"media":{"__typename":"ComponentsImage","src":"https://c.files.bbci.co.uk/1226D/production/_105894347_grey_line-nc.png","srcSet":"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/1226D/production/_105894347_grey_line-nc.png 240w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/1226D/production/_105894347_grey_line-nc.png 320w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/1226D/production/_105894347_grey_line-nc.png 480w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/1226D/production/_105894347_grey_line-nc.png 624w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/1226D/production/_105894347_grey_line-nc.png 800w","height":2,"width":640,"alt":"2px presentational grey line","loading":"lazy"}}},{"type":"image","model":{"emphasiseImage":false,"media":{"__typename":"ComponentsImage","src":"https://c.files.bbci.co.uk/1156F/production/_112832017__104759123_laurakuenssberg_tr-nc.png","srcSet":"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/1156F/production/_112832017__104759123_laurakuenssberg_tr-nc.png 240w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/1156F/production/_112832017__104759123_laurakuenssberg_tr-nc.png 320w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/1156F/production/_112832017__104759123_laurakuenssberg_tr-nc.png 480w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/1156F/production/_112832017__104759123_laurakuenssberg_tr-nc.png 624w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/1156F/production/_112832017__104759123_laurakuenssberg_tr-nc.png 800w","height":340,"width":1706,"alt":"Analysis box by Laura Kuenssberg, political editor","loading":"lazy"}}},{"type":"text","model":{"blocks":[{"type":"paragraph","model":{"text":"It's a complicated equation. The Department of Health is worried about the spread of the disease, as well as other patients losing out on other treatments because of the focus on Covid. ","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"It's a complicated equation. The Department of Health is worried about the spread of the disease, as well as other patients losing out on other treatments because of the focus on Covid. ","attributes":[]}}]}}]}},{"type":"text","model":{"blocks":[{"type":"paragraph","model":{"text":"No 11 is fearful about the impact on the economy, which has already had a profound shock. ","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"No 11 is fearful about the impact on the economy, which has already had a profound shock. ","attributes":[]}}]}}]}},{"type":"text","model":{"blocks":[{"type":"paragraph","model":{"text":"And it's No 10's job to worry about all of it, then reach a conclusion.  ","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"And it's No 10's job to worry about all of it, then reach a conclusion.  ","attributes":[]}}]}}]}},{"type":"text","model":{"blocks":[{"type":"paragraph","model":{"text":"But Boris Johnson also knows that his own MPs and the opposition parties are more and more sceptical as each day passes about what the government proposes. ","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"But Boris Johnson also knows that his own MPs and the opposition parties are more and more sceptical as each day passes about what the government proposes. ","attributes":[]}}]}}]}},{"type":"text","model":{"blocks":[{"type":"paragraph","model":{"text":"It's clear that shutting pubs and restaurants is a possibility - the \"circuit breaker\" that we have talked about lots of times. ","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"It's clear that shutting pubs and restaurants is a possibility - the \"circuit breaker\" that we have talked about lots of times. ","attributes":[]}}]}}]}},{"type":"text","model":{"blocks":[{"type":"paragraph","model":{"text":"But there are many questions still to be settled.  ","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"But there are many questions still to be settled.  ","attributes":[]}}]}}]}},{"type":"text","model":{"blocks":[{"type":"paragraph","model":{"text":"Read more from Laura here.","blocks":[{"type":"urlLink","model":{"text":"Read more from Laura here","locator":"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-54456303","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"Read more from Laura here","attributes":[]}}]}},{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":".","attributes":[]}}]}}]}},{"type":"image","model":{"emphasiseImage":false,"media":{"__typename":"ComponentsImage","src":"https://c.files.bbci.co.uk/1226D/production/_105894347_grey_line-nc.png","srcSet":"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/1226D/production/_105894347_grey_line-nc.png 240w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/1226D/production/_105894347_grey_line-nc.png 320w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/1226D/production/_105894347_grey_line-nc.png 480w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/1226D/production/_105894347_grey_line-nc.png 624w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/1226D/production/_105894347_grey_line-nc.png 800w","height":2,"width":640,"alt":"2px presentational grey line","loading":"lazy"}}},{"type":"text","model":{"blocks":[{"type":"paragraph","model":{"text":"The planned tightening of restrictions in parts of England follows rising infection rates across much of the country, with the Academy of Medical Colleges warning the NHS is at risk of becoming overwhelmed.","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"The planned tightening of restrictions in parts of England follows rising infection rates across much of the country, with the Academy of Medical Colleges warning the NHS is at risk of becoming overwhelmed.","attributes":[]}}]}}]}},{"type":"text","model":{"blocks":[{"type":"paragraph","model":{"text":"Nottingham, Knowsley, Liverpool, Manchester and Newcastle upon Tyne have the highest infection rates in England, according to the latest Public Health England data.","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"Nottingham, Knowsley, Liverpool, Manchester and Newcastle upon Tyne have the highest infection rates in England, according to the latest Public Health England data.","attributes":[]}}]}}]}},{"type":"text","model":{"blocks":[{"type":"paragraph","model":{"text":"From Friday, all pubs and restaurants across central Scotland, including Glasgow and Edinburgh, are to close, while in the rest of Scotland hospitality venues must shut at 18:00 BS